# Seed conventions (core-be)

Owner: **[seed-maintainer](../skills/seed-maintainer/SKILL.md)** — full layout, contract, idempotency, and tier rules live there (and in `src/scripts/seed/seed.overview.md`).

- Every folder that **owns tables** (domain / sub-domain / nested) gets a co-located `seed/` dir (`*.reference.seed.ts`, `*.bulk.seed.ts`, `*.faker.ts`, `index.ts`); table-less folders have none.
- Each `seed/index.ts` exports a `SeedContribution`; a **domain root** exports a `DomainSeedModule` (`name` + `dependsOn`) — the only unit the orchestrator (`src/scripts/seed/bulk.ts`) registers and topo-orders. Contract: `src/scripts/seed/seed-contract.ts`.
- Seed **only your own tables**; cross-domain parent ids flow via the `SeedRegistry` on `SeedContext`.
- **Idempotent** re-runs required; the production guard `assertBulkSeedAllowed` must never be weakened.
